title: Spacious 1 Bedroom in Hopkins
posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OIB/NJRS', 'Westside Village Apartments offers 16 different floor plans to choose from.', 'Enjoy underground heated parking, private patios/balconies, an outdoor pool, playground, fitness center, professional on-site management and maintenance, and a controlled entry.', 'Fiber-optic internet service is available!', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call Westside Village home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Homes may have 1 - 1.5 bath depending on the model', 'Appliances in kitchen', 'Balcony or patio options', 'Fiber-optic internet service available', 'Smoke free', 'Walk-in closet', 'Wall air conditioning', 'Window coverings', 'Community Amenities', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', 'Elevator access', 'Trash chutes', 'Laundry facility', 'Additional storage', 'Fitness center', 'Outdoor swimming pool', 'Party room', 'Off street parking', 'Playground', 'BBQ & picnic area', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Westside Village Apartments Information', 'Address:', '101 Blake Rd N, Hopkins MN, 55343', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=28', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Application Fee:', '$45', 'Pet Fee:', '$100 - 200 (Note: varies with type of pet)', 'Pet Deposit:', '$200', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Saturday:', '10:00AM - 5:00PM', 'Sunday:', '11:00AM - 4:00PM']
